<!-- Cinematic Privacy Policy Page -->
<div class="min-h-screen bg-primary-950 relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Ambient Background Glows -->
    <div
        class="absolute top-0 right-0 -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-purple-600/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full pointer-events-none animate-drift">
    </div>
    <div
        class="absolute bottom-1/4 left-0 -translate-x-1/2 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-pink-600/5 blur-[100px] rounded-full pointer-events-none animate-swell">
    </div>

    <style>
        @keyframes drift {

            0%,
            100% {
                transform: translate(50%, -50%) scale(1);
            }

            50% {
                transform: translate(45%, -45%) scale(1.1);
            }
        }

        @keyframes swell {

            0%,
            100% {
                transform: translate(-50%, 0) scale(1);
                opacity: 0.4;
            }

            50% {
                transform: translate(-45%, 5%) scale(1.15);
                opacity: 0.6;
            }
        }

        .animate-drift {
            animation: drift 20s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .animate-swell {
            animation: swell 25s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .stroke-text {
            -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            color: transparent;
        }
    </style>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 py-16 relative z-10">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">

            <!-- Mega Header -->
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-[10px] font-black text-purple-500 uppercase tracking-[0.5em] mb-3 italic">Kebijakan</h2>
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white uppercase italic tracking-tighter leading-none">
                    <span class="stroke-text">Privasi</span> Kamu
                </h1>
            </div>

            <!-- Content -->
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <section class="bg-[#1a1625]/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/5 p-8">
                    <p class="text-white/40 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest leading-loose italic">
                        Di Komikkuya, privasi kamu adalah prioritas kami. Kebijakan Privasi ini menjelaskan bagaimana
                        kami mengumpulkan, menggunakan, dan melindungi informasi kamu saat menggunakan website kami
                        untuk baca komik.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="bg-[#1a1625]/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/5 p-8">
                    <h3 class="text-xs font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wider italic mb-4">1. Data yang Kami
                        Kumpulkan</h3>
                    <p class="text-white/40 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest leading-loose italic mb-4">
                        Saat kamu baca komik di Komikkuya, kami mungkin mengumpulkan:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-500 mt-1.5 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                            <span class="text-white/30 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest italic">Info
                                device kamu (browser, sistem operasi)</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-500 mt-1.5 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                            <span class="text-white/30 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest italic">Alamat IP
                                (buat deteksi VPN dan keamanan)</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-500 mt-1.5 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                            <span class="text-white/30 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest italic">Riwayat
                                baca komik kamu (disimpan di browser lokal)</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-500 mt-1.5 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                            <span class="text-white/30 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest italic">Daftar
                                favorit komik (disimpan di browser lokal)</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="bg-[#1a1625]/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/5 p-8">
                    <h3 class="text-xs font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wider italic mb-4">2. Gimana Kami Pakai
                        Data</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-500 mt-1.5 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                            <span class="text-white/30 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest italic">Biar kamu
                                bisa lanjut baca dari chapter terakhir</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-500 mt-1.5 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                            <span class="text-white/30 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest italic">Nyimpen
                                daftar komik favorit kamu</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-500 mt-1.5 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                            <span class="text-white/30 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest italic">Kasih
                                rekomendasi yang sesuai selera kamu</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-500 mt-1.5 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                            <span class="text-white/30 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest italic">Deteksi
                                dan cegah spam atau abuse</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="bg-[#1a1625]/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/5 p-8">
                    <h3 class="text-xs font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wider italic mb-4">3. Cookies & Local
                        Storage</h3>
                    <p class="text-white/40 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest leading-loose italic">
                        Kami pakai cookies dan local storage buat nyimpen preferensi kamu, kayak riwayat baca dan daftar
                        favorit. Data ini disimpan di browser kamu sendiri, bukan di server kami. Kamu bisa hapus kapan
                        aja lewat pengaturan browser.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="bg-[#1a1625]/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/5 p-8">
                    <h3 class="text-xs font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wider italic mb-4">4. Keamanan Data</h3>
                    <p class="text-white/40 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest leading-loose italic">
                        Kami nggak nyimpen data sensitif kamu di server kami. Semua data kayak riwayat baca dan favorit
                        disimpan secara lokal di browser kamu. Kami juga pakai HTTPS buat enkripsi semua traffic.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="bg-[#1a1625]/60 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/5 p-8">
                    <h3 class="text-xs font-black text-white uppercase tracking-wider italic mb-4">5. Ada Pertanyaan?
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-white/40 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest leading-loose italic">
                        Kalau ada pertanyaan soal privasi, langsung aja hubungi kami lewat <a href="/contact"
                            class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300">halaman kontak</a>.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <!-- Footer -->
                <div class="text-center pt-8 border-t border-white/5">
                    <p class="text-white/20 text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] italic">
                        Terakhir diperbarui: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('id-ID') %>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>